u can find the source code on GitHub at https://github.com/applied-systems-biology/jipipe.
Logos If you need the JIPipe logo for presentations, posters, or publications, feel free to download the logo package. It contains the JIPipe logos (text plus logo, square logo) in PNG and SVG formats.
